#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Hardware tab"
msgstr "Kaart Riistvara"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actual effect of setting these options depends upon the features "
"provided by your keyboard hardware and the X server on which &plasma; is "
"running. As an example, you may find that changing the key click volume has "
"no effect because that feature is not available on your system."
msgstr ""
"Siinsete valikute tegelik toime sõltub sellest, mida võimaldab klaviatuur "
"ise ning X'i server, millel &plasma; töötab. Näiteks võid avastada, et "
"klahvivajutuse helitugevuse muutmine ei mõju kuidagi, sest süsteem seda ei "
"võimaldagi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard model:"
msgstr "Klaviatuuri mudel:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Here you can set your keyboard model. This setting is independent of your "
#| "keyboard layout and refers to the &quot;hardware&quot; model, i.e. the "
#| "way your keyboard is manufactured. Modern keyboards that come with your "
#| "computer usually have two extra keys and are referred to as &quot;104-"
#| "key&quot; models, which is probably what you want if you do not know what "
#| "kind of keyboard you have."
msgid ""
"Here you can set your keyboard model. This setting is independent of your "
"keyboard layout and refers to the &quot;hardware&quot; model, &ie; the way "
"your keyboard is manufactured. Modern keyboards that come with your computer "
"usually have two extra keys and are referred to as &quot;104-key&quot; "
"models, which is probably what you want if you do not know what kind of "
"keyboard you have."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab valida klaviatuuri mudeli. See seadistus ei ole seotud sinu "
"klaviatuuripaigutusega ning tähistab ainult klaviatuuri &quot;"
"riistvara&quot; mudelit, s.t viisi, kuidas sinu klaviatuur on toodetud. "
"Kaasajal toodetavad klaviatuurid, mida müüakse koos arvutitega, on kahe "
"lisaklahviga ning tähistatakse kui &quot;104-klahviga&quot; mudelid. See on "
"valik, mida sa ilmselt pead kasutama, kui täpselt ei tea, mis tüüpi "
"klaviatuur sul on."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "NumLock on Plasma Startup"
msgstr "NumLock Plasma käivitamisel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to either always <guilabel>Turn on</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Turn off</guilabel> the NumLock when &plasma; starts, or you can "
"choose to have &plasma; leave NumLock at whatever it was set to before "
"&plasma; started up."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab valida, kas NumLock <guilabel>lülitatakse sisse</guilabel> või "
"<guilabel>lülitatakse välja</guilabel> &plasma; käivitamisel või jäetakse "
"hoopis kehtima NumLock'i see olek, mis kehtis enne &plasma; käivitamist."

